com.tractrac.ResultAPI
Class LiveResult

java.lang.Object
  com.tractrac.ResultAPI.LiveResult

public class LiveResult
extends java.lang.Object

A class representing a live result for sailing The result compares boats on all legs. The live result is limited to one class.
